T02TD2765E:141b-1: rje chen po mchod sbyin gyi dbang po la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2765E:141b-3: gtso bo mchod bya mchod sbyin bzhes //
T02TD2765E:141b-4: zhes 'byung ba'i sgrub thabs bshad par bya'o //
T02TD2765E:141b-5: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dpal nyid //
T02TD2765E:141b-6: gtsor bcas sangs rgyas sras bcas la //
T02TD2765E:141b-7: dad pas skyabs su song nas ni //
T02TD2765E:141b-8: snying rje chen pos gtor ma sbyin //
T02TD2765E:141b-9: bdag nyid lha yi rnal 'byor pas //
T02TD2765E:141b-10: lce dang lag pa snod dang bcud //
T02TD2765E:141b-11: gsang sngags rgyal pos byin brlabs la //
T02TD2765E:141b-12: gzi bskyed zab cing rgya ches mchod //
T02TD2765E:141b-14: aa a'a ai a'i au a'u /
T02TD2765E:141b-18: aam aa: lce byin gyis brlab pa'o //
T02TD2765E:141b-26: sha sha sa ha ksha: lag pa byin gyis brlab pa'o //
T02TD2765E:141b-27: h'um katsa ta ta pa ya sha ksha:/
T02TD2765E:141b-29: aoma'a:h'um bam to:gzi byin bskyed pa'o//
T02TD2765E:141b-30: aom aa k'a ro mu kham sarbba dharm'a n'am /
T02TD2765E:141b-31: a'adya nutpanna tv'ata bi shuddha sv'a h'a /
T02TD2765E:141b-33: aom a'a: hr'i: sarba ta th'a ga to aa dhishth'a na sarba p'u dza me gha sa mu dra spha ra na mu tra dridha h'um /
T02TD2765E:141b-35: aom a'a:hr'i:shr'i lo ka n'a tha sarba buddha bo dhi satva sa ka la aishta de ba ta sarba dharm'a p'a la pushpam /
T02TD2765E:141b-45: sarba gardza pa ri pu dyam /
T02TD2765E:141b-46: me ma raksha h'um h'um phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD2765E:141b-47: dbul ba dang las bcol ba'i sngags so //
T02TD2765E:141b-50: legs bskor 'od zer ljags sbubs kyis //
T02TD2765E:141b-51: bdud rtsi'i gtor ma bzhes par 'gyur //
T02TD2765E:141b-52: thugs rje chen po'i gtor ma'i cho ga rdzogs so//
